CREATE TABLE products (
    id SERIAL,
    product_name VARCHAR(255),
    price DECIMAL(10, 2),
    category VARCHAR(50),
    manufacturer VARCHAR(100),
    created_at TIMESTAMP,
    PRIMARY KEY (id)
)
